<view class="page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="hero-icon">？</view>
    <view class="hero-title">我们能帮您什么？</view>
    <view class="hero-sub">浏览常见问题或直接向我们发送反馈建议。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-head">常见问题</view>
    <view class="faq">
      <view class="faq-item">
        <view class="faq-title">如何上传照片？</view>
        <view class="faq-desc">选择“修复”功能，点击中心框选区域即可从相册选取。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="faq-item">
        <view class="faq-title">支付问题？</view>
        <view class="faq-desc">请检查微信支付历史记录，或在账号页面尝试恢复购买。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="faq-item">
        <view class="faq-title">我的修复记录在哪？</view>
        <view class="faq-desc">您可以在“修复记录”标签页查看所有之前的修复过的图片。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="faq-item">
        <view class="faq-title">画质设置？</view>
        <view class="faq-desc">目前提供“画质增强”和“黑白上色”，后续会支持更多精细参数。</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-head">提交反馈</view>
    <view class="form">
      <view class="form-row">
        <view class="label">问题类型</view>
        <picker class="picker" range="{{types}}" value="{{typeIndex}}" bindchange="onTypeChange">
          <view class="picker-value">{{types[typeIndex]}}</view>
        </picker>
        <view class="chev">⌄</view>
      </view>
      <view class="divider"></view>
      <view class="form-row col">
        <view class="label">详细描述</view>
        <textarea class="textarea" value="{{content}}" bindinput="onContentInput" placeholder="请详细描述您遇到的问题或建议..." maxlength="500"></textarea>
      </view>
    </view>
    <button class="submit-btn" bindtap="onSubmit" loading="{{submitting}}" disabled="{{submitting}}">提交反馈</button>
    <view wx:if="{{showSubmitSuccessTip && lastFeedbackId}}" class="submit-success-card">
      <view class="submit-success-title">反馈已提交，可继续联系客服</view>
      <view class="submit-success-desc">复制反馈编号后，点击下方“联系客服”，客服侧可更快定位你的问题。</view>
      <view class="feedback-id-row">
        <view class="feedback-id-text">反馈编号：{{lastFeedbackId}}</view>
        <button class="copy-btn" bindtap="onCopyFeedbackId">复制编号</button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="support">
    <view class="support-left">
      <view class="support-title">需要人工支持？</view>
      <view class="support-desc">进入微信客服会话，自动带上当前页面和最近一次反馈信息。</view>
      <view wx:if="{{lastFeedbackId}}" class="support-note">最近反馈编号：{{lastFeedbackId}}</view>
    </view>
    <button class="support-btn" open-type="contact" session-from="{{contactSessionFrom}}">联系客服</button>
  </view>
</view>
